---
import LinkedInIcon from "../icons/SocialIcons/LinkedInIcon.astro";
import GithubIcon from "../icons/SocialIcons/GithubIcon.astro";
import GmailIcon from "../icons/SocialIcons/GmailIcon.astro";
import FileDownload from "../icons/FileDownload.astro";
---
   <div class="grid max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-8 mx-auto lg:gap-8 xl:gap-0 lg:py-16 lg:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="mr-auto place-self-center lg:col-span-7">
            <h1 class="max-w-2xl mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none md:text-3xl xl:text-3xl dark:text-white"> Juan Pablo Riglos <span class="text-orange-300"> Frontend Developer </span></h1>
            <p class="max-w-2xl mb-6 font-light  lg:mb-8 md:text-lg lg:text-lg text-light-400"> Gracias por leer, te cuento, si bien tengo un titulo de abogado, hoy dia soy un profesional del desarrollo web, abocado principalmente al Frontend, y especializado en React.js particularmente, como asi tambien toda herramienta de la cual se sustente para crear soluciones webs cada vez mas robustas y eficacez.</p>
            <p class="text-orange-300"> Me caracterizo por estar en la busqueda constante de nuevas oportunidades y conocimientos</p>
            
        </div>
        <div class="m-auto lg:mt-0 lg:col-span-5 lg:flex">
            <img class="h-[350px] m-6 rounded-xl opacity-40 hover:opacity-90 hover:cursor-help"  src="/misimagenes/conMate.jpg" alt="mockup">
        </div>                
    </div>
    <nav class=" mx-auto flex gap-4 justify-around">
        <div class="pillShadow size-auto pl-2 rounded-xl bg-gray-700/30 opacity-55 flex items-center justify-between overflow-hidden gap-3 hover:text-gray-100 hover:opacity-90"> <a href="https://github.com/JuanPabloRiglos" target="_blank">Github </a> <GithubIcon class="size-6"/> </div>
        <div class="pillShadow size-auto pl-2 rounded-xl bg-gray-700/30 opacity-55 flex items-center justify-between overflow-hidden gap-3  hover:text-gray-100 hover:opacity-90"> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/juanpabloriglos/" target="_blank"> Linkedin </a><LinkedInIcon class="size-6 rounded-xl"/> </div>
        <div class="pillShadow size-auto pl-2 rounded-xl bg-gray-700/30 opacity-55 flex items-center justify-between overflow-hidden gap-3  hover:text-gray-100 hover:opacity-90">juanpabloriglos@gmail.com <GmailIcon class="size-6 rounded-xl"/> </div>
        <div class="pillShadow size-auto pl-2 rounded-xl bg-gray-700/30 opacity-55 flex items-center justify-between overflow-hidden gap-3  hover:text-gray-100 hover:opacity-90 hover:cursor-pointer"> Descarga CV <FileDownload class="size-6 rounded-xl  text-orange-300"/> </div>
    
    </nav>


    <style>
        .pillShadow:hover{
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}
    </style>